{"tid":2320926,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"尹兆堅：政府用《國安法》告黎智英後有可能凍結資產 令蘋果經營更困難","createTime":"2020-12-11T07:26:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T08:03:47.000Z","uid":22556,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"67cfa9b5a5e8f2580961fec59afc76da50a0004d","tid":2320926,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T07:26:17.000Z","msg":"正被關押的壹傳媒創辦人黎智英今日中午被警方加控一項「勾結外國或者境外勢力危害國家安全」罪，案件將於明日早上於西九龍裁判法院提堂。《港區國安法》除了有不准保釋、長期監禁等招數外，另一殺着是凍結資產。民主黨前立法會議員尹兆堅憂慮，今次當局加控壹傳媒創辦人黎智英勾結外國勢力罪，背後用意「就係要除咗政府嘅眼中釘」，令《蘋果》滅聲。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201211/TXKT3IO6C5AAXMFWRJP4IEVEAM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201211%2FTXKT3IO6C5AAXMFWRJP4IEVEAM%2F&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2WrppvqZ4W3gw9R4Gr2eBBN4Jm0fY%3D&h=fd6fb080\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201211%2FTXKT3IO6C5AAXMFWRJP4IEVEAM%2F&h=728afc98\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201211/TXKT3IO6C5AAXMFWRJP4IEVEAM/</a>"},{"pid":"ffc78952d0b97d01ffe3f846bb3c2c4d087e3f4a","tid":2320926,"uid":296830,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T07:33:16.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">北東廠叫做嘢、国安處收到柯打、傀儡政權𠵱家有權用盡，凡喺反對嘅，會打壓到冇得反抗！</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/vampire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/vampire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11ae7b4bfab2b00e121904d4c4eeee215a0236fd","tid":2320926,"uid":277702,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T07:55:37.000Z","msg":"咁搞呀栗頭一定比美國佬落鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fff453f6516039763eca0aff4a02644fb6dcaae3","tid":2320926,"uid":60057,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T08:03:47.000Z","msg":"柒頭：「本身都諗唔到，俾你講一講又好似有計咁喎」"}]}